The paper also involves the use of random codes and decoding algorithms, which are topics in data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper also discusses lower bounds on the capacity of channels, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
